OL,5,G0035 Life on Earth
OL,6,     F2/13. David Attenborough examines
OL,7,     Fthe creatures and fossils of the
OL,8,     FGreat Barrier Reef, which provide
OL,9,     Fclues to how the original
OL,10,     Fprimitive animals of the sea
OL,11,     Fevolved.
OL,12,G0130 Voyages of Discovery
OL,13,     FPaul Rose reveals the story behind
OL,14,     Fthe first ever circumnavigation of
OL,15,     Fthe world, when Magellan set out
OL,16,     F500 years ago to find the westward
OL,17,     Froute to the Spice Islands.
